These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: lemon, tomato, watermelon, apple, orange, mango, artichoke
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, january, june, may, april, july, november
7 different games are played: whist, go, backgammon, snooker, poker, billiard, bridge
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is the dutch##1
 3. the person playing poker is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the british is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person eating tomato is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person playing snooker is between the person playing bridge and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person eating watermelon is in the middle##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is the person eating orange##1
12. the person eating orange is the person playing whist##1
13. the person eating lemon is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the person playing backgammon##1
15. the person playing billiard is on the left of the german##1
16. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating mango##1
17. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Food      | tomato  | mango        | orange | watermelon      | apple     | lemon      | artichoke     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Birthday         | june | april | october | january | november  | july  | may    |
| Game     | poker  | billiard         | whist     | go    | backgammon | snooker     | bridge     |

