.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, chess, cooking, camping, fishing, card-games, photography
The people have 7 different jobs:  journalist, coach, electrician, writer, bartender, security-guard, engineer
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: marigold, dahlia, aconite, bellflower, daffodil, poppy, sunflower
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, car, helicopter, quad-bike, roller, ship, skateboard
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is the writer##1
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the bartender##1
 3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 4. the coach is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the electrician##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the security-guard is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who growsaconite and the engineer##2
11. the person who growsdahlia is the writer##1
12. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
13. the person who growsdaffodil is between the engineer and the person who growspoppy##2
14. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
17. the journalist is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
18. the coach is on the left of the electrician##1
19. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
20. the electrician is between the person driving the ship and the coach##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7     |
