 9. the person playing scrabble is the davidoff-smoker##1
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
11. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who growspoppy##1
12. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
13. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
14. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person playing poker##1
15. the person playing go is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
